h1.font: Step4a: Map N-side child attributes to 1-side parent attributes as FKs

p.span: N-side relations get the FK to the 1-side PK.

p.font: In this case, we must map the parent entity EMPLOYEE.SSN to itself and add an additional column for the child entity FK EMPLOYEE.Super_ssn. This is called a recursive relationship.
